{"type":"message","id":"615fbd8c","parentId":"b449afae","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:44:02.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a7381f2013991140169c67b8f3c1c819188da7f2943889421\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6pbscl3zEU4dHG1suALUNZOS|fc_0a7381f2013991140169c67b93cf188191b25d53caae9132ba","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-27.md","content":"## Preference learned — task progress updates\n\nLucca wants explicit progress communication for spawned subagents / longer tasks:\n- always notify when a launched task/subagent is finished\n- while still running, send an update every 10 minutes\n- applies to cases like spawned subagents or long-running background tasks\n\nOperational implication for Tobias:\n- do not silently leave background work running without status\n- if runtime/tooling cannot support exact timed pushes automatically, state that clearly and emulate as closely as possible when possible\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\memory\\\\2026-03-27.md\",\"content\":\"## Preference learned — task progress updates\\n\\nLucca wants explicit progress communication for spawned subagents / longer tasks:\\n- always notify when a launched task/subagent is finished\\n- while still running, send an update every 10 minutes\\n- applies to cases like spawned subagents or long-running background tasks\\n\\nOperational implication for Tobias:\\n- do not silently leave background work running without status\\n- if runtime/tooling cannot support exact timed pushes automatically, state that clearly and emulate as closely as possible when possible\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kRCREnPX2zK9gcyqSiyjvizl|fc_0a7381f2013991140169c67b93cf288191a2605e28843e1429","name":"edit","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md","oldText":"## 🧠 Lições Apren