{"type":"message","id":"942db39e","parentId":"ccb81636","timestamp":"2026-03-27T17:58:47.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Dei o pontapé inicial do watchdog.\n\n## O que já foi criado\nEm:\n\n`C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\`\n\njá estão:\n- `config.json`\n- `active_tasks.json`\n- `README.md`\n- `watchdog.py`\n\n## O que o watchdog já faz\n- lê o registry global de tarefas\n- atualiza `lastCheckedAt`\n- decide se deve:\n  - mandar aviso de tarefa rodando\n  - mandar aviso de tarefa concluída\n  - mandar alerta de falha\n- remove tarefas concluídas/falhadas do active registry\n- formata mensagens em **texto humano**\n- já inclui **modelo** na mensagem\n- já trata datas em formato legível\n\n## Teste inicial\nRodei o script agora e ele respondeu correctamente com:\n\n- sem tarefas activas\n- sem notificações\n- registry limpo\n\nOu seja: **o núcleo determinístico do watchdog já está em pé.**\n\n---\n\n## Ajuste pequeno que apareceu\nTentei também criar o ficheiro:\n- `task_history.jsonl`\n\nmas a escrita vazia falhou por detalhe do tool.  \nÉ detalhe pequeno, eu corrijo no próximo passo sem drama.\n\n---\n\n## O que ainda falta para o MVP ficar útil de verdade\nAgora entram as peças importantes:\n\n### 1. registrar tarefas automaticamente\nHoje o watchdog existe, mas eu ainda preciso ligar o launch das tarefas ao registry.\n\nOu seja:\n- spawn → registrar em `active_tasks.json`\n\n### 2. criar um pequeno helper de registro\nAlgo tipo:\n- adicionar tarefa nova\n- atualizar status\n- marcar concluída/falha\n\n### 3. ligar isso ao cron / monitor periódico\nAí sim ele passa a funcionar sozinho no ritmo:\n- check 5 min\n- avisa 10 min\n\n### 4. decidir como o watchdog entrega a mensagem\nO script hoje **gera as notificações**.\nAinda falta decidir o melhor caminho para o OpenClaw pegar isso e te mandar no chat automaticamente.\n\n---\n\n## Estado honesto agora\n### já pronto\n- estrutura base\n- script watchdog funcional\n- formatação humana\n- suporte a modelo/timestamps legíveis\n\n### ainda não pronto\n- auto-registro no launch\n- histórico\n- cron ligado\n- entrega automática da mensagem no Telegram\n\nSe quiser, eu sigo agora para a **segunda parte: integrar o registry com as tarefas lançadas por mim**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a7381f2013991140169c6c54e9e4c8191b0f973f596e2ef97\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":227,"output":516,"cacheRead":159872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":160615,"cost":{"input":0.0005675000000000001,"output":0.00774,"cacheRead":0.039968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0482755}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774634314272,"responseId":"resp_0a7381f2013991140169c6c54b60708191adfa0b64a76e1f1a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5e72ebe","parentId":"942db39e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T17:59:36.340Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"143\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1962323981\",\n  \"sender\": \"Lucca Werner\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-27 14:59 GMT-3\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Lucca Werner (1962323981)\",\n  \"id\": \"1962323981\",\n  \"name\": \"Lucca Werner\"\n}\n```\n\nSe quiser, eu sigo agora para a segunda parte: integrar o registry com as tarefas lançadas por mim. > Pode fazewr"}],"timestamp":1774634376334}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9de3a2d","parentId":"b5e72ebe","timestamp":"2026-03-27T17:59:53.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a7381f2013991140169c6c58ba0388191a2980149afeb581b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_MhnApGlM9460Z5QER13Q7Spm|fc_0a7381f2013991140169c6c599f8b481919cdad1f8b74e0b66","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\task_history.jsonl","content":"\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\task_watchdog\\\\task_history.jsonl\",\"content\":\"\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_BURQLWwHDmGz4IlMCVOdnsC8|fc_0a7381f2013991140169c6c599f8cc8191ab5ba1cf239dd272","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\registry_helpers.py","content":"from __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional\n\nBASE = Path(r\"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\")\nACTIVE_PATH = BASE / \"active_tasks.json\"\nHISTORY_PATH = BASE / \"task_history.jsonl\"\n\n\ndef now_iso() -> str:\n    return datetime.now(timezone.utc).astimezone().isoformat()\n\n\ndef load_active() -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n    if not ACTIVE_PATH.exists():\n        return []\n    try:\n        return json.loads(ACTIVE_PATH.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    except Exception:\n        return []\n\n\ndef save_active(tasks: List[Dict[str, Any]]) -> None:\n    ACTIVE_PATH.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    tmp = ACTIVE_PATH.with_suffix(\".json.tmp\")\n    tmp.write_text(json.dumps(tasks, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    tmp.replace(ACTIVE_PATH)\n\n\ndef append_history(entry: Dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    HISTORY_PATH.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with HISTORY_PATH.open(\"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        f.write(json.dumps(entry, ensure_ascii=False) + \"\\n\")\n\n\ndef register_task(task: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    tasks = load_active()\n    task.setdefault(\"startedAt\", now_iso())\n    task.setdefault(\"lastCheckedAt\", None)\n    task.setdefault(\"lastNotifiedAt\", None)\n    task.setdefault(\"notifyEveryMinutes\", 10)\n    task.setdefault(\"status\", \"running\")\n    task.setdefault(\"launcher\", \"Tobias\")\n    tasks.append(task)\n    save_active(tasks)\n    return task\n\n\ndef update_task(task_id: str, **fields: Any) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]:\n    tasks = load_active()\n    updated = None\n    for task in tasks:\n        if task.get(\"taskId\") == task_id:\n            task.update(fields)\n            updated = task\n            break\n    save_active(tasks)\n    return updated\n\n\ndef finish_task(task_id: str, status: str = \"completed\", result_summary: Optional[str] = None, error: Optional[str] = None) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]:\n    tasks = load_active()\n    remaining = []\n    finished = None\n    for task in tasks:\n        if task.get(\"taskId\") == task_id:\n            task[\"status\"] = status\n            task[\"endedAt\"] = now_iso()\n            if result_summary is not None:\n                task[\"resultSummary\"] = result_summary\n            if error is not None:\n                task[\"error\"] = error\n            finished = task\n            append_history(task)\n        else:\n            remaining.append(task)\n    save_active(remaining)\n    return finished\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\task_watchdog\\\\registry_helpers.py\",\"content\":\"from __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport json\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional\\n\\nBASE = Path(r\\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\task_watchdog\\\")\\nACTIVE_PATH = BASE / \\\"active_tasks.json\\\"\\nHISTORY_PATH = BASE / \\\"task_history.jsonl\\\"\\n\\n\\ndef now_iso() -> str:\\n    return datetime.now(timezone.utc).astimezone().isoformat()\\n\\n\\ndef load_active() -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\\n    if not ACTIVE_PATH.exists():\\n        return []\\n    try:\\n        return json.loads(ACTIVE_PATH.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\"))\\n    except Exception:\\n        return []\\n\\n\\ndef save_active(tasks: List[Dict[str, Any]]) -> None:\\n    ACTIVE_PATH.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\\n    tmp = ACTIVE_PATH.with_suffix(\\\".json.tmp\\\")\\n    tmp.write_text(json.dumps(tasks, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\")\\n    tmp.replace(ACTIVE_PATH)\\n\\n\\ndef append_history(entry: Dict[str, Any]) -> None:\\n    HISTORY_PATH.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\\n    with HISTORY_PATH.open(\\\"a\\\", encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\") as f:\\n        f.write(json.dumps(entry, ensure_ascii=False) + \\\"\\\\n\\\")\\n\\n\\ndef register_task(task: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]:\\n    tasks = load_active()\\n    task.setdefault(\\\"startedAt\\\", now_iso())\\n    task.setdefault(\\\"lastCheckedAt\\\", None)\\n    task.setdefault(\\\"lastNotifiedAt\\\", None)\\n    task.setdefault(\\\"notifyEveryMinutes\\\", 10)\\n    task.setdefault(\\\"status\\\", \\\"running\\\")\\n    task.setdefault(\\\"launcher\\\", \\\"Tobias\\\")\\n    tasks.append(task)\\n    save_active(tasks)\\n    return task\\n\\n\\ndef update_task(task_id: str, **fields: Any) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]:\\n    tasks = load_active()\\n    updated = None\\n    for task in tasks:\\n        if task.get(\\\"taskId\\\") == task_id:\\n            task.update(fields)\\n            updated = task\\n            break\\n    save_active(tasks)\\n    return updated\\n\\n\\ndef finish_task(task_id: str, status: str = \\\"completed\\\", result_summary: Optional[str] = None, error: Optional[str] = None) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]:\\n    tasks = load_active()\\n    remaining = []\\n    finished = None\\n    for task in tasks:\\n        if task.get(\\\"taskId\\\") == task_id:\\n            task[\\\"status\\\"] = status\\n            task[\\\"endedAt\\\"] = now_iso()\\n            if result_summary is not None:\\n                task[\\\"resultSummary\\\"] = result_summary\\n            if error is not None:\\n                task[\\\"error\\\"] = error\\n            finished = task\\n            append_history(task)\\n        else:\\n            remaining.append(task)\\n    save_active(remaining)\\n    return finished\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":245,"output":788,"cacheRead":160512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":161545,"cost":{"input":0.0006125000000000001,"output":0.01182,"cacheRead":0.040128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.052560499999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774634376340,"responseId":"resp_0a7381f2013991140169c6c589ba1c81919eaf1d30006aee6c"}}
