{"type":"message","id":"c69dd6b4","parentId":"ced5b214","timestamp":"2026-03-27T21:05:47.908Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6KgzGYeBHfEGVygmJXZXbUFb|fc_0a7381f2013991140169c6f12aa5bc8191a17f86482d2900dc","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-03-27.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 11,\n      \"score\": 0.25324728488922116,\n      \"snippet\": \"## Preference learned — task progress updates\\n\\nLucca wants explicit progress communication for spawned subagents / longer tasks:\\n- always notify when a launched task/subagent is finished\\n- while still running, send an update every 10 minutes\\n- applies to cases like spawned subagents or long-running background tasks\\n\\nOperational implication for Tobias:\\n- do not silently leave background work running without status\\n- if runtime/tooling cannot support exact timed pushes automatically, state that clearly and emulate as closely as possible when possible\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-03-27.md#L1-L11\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-03-27.md#L1-L11\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"openai\",\n  \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"hybrid\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"path":"memory/2026-03-27.md","startLine":1,"endLine":11,"score":0.25324728488922116,"snippet":"## Preference learned — task progress updates\n\nLucca wants explicit progress communication for spawned subagents / longer tasks:\n- always notify when a launched task/subagent is finished\n- while still running, send an update every 10 minutes\n- applies to cases like spawned subagents or long-running background tasks\n\nOperational implication for Tobias:\n- do not silently leave background work running without status\n- if runtime/tooling cannot support exact timed pushes automatically, state that clearly and emulate as closely as possible when possible\n\nSourc