{"type":"message","id":"7582fbbf","parentId":"36b3a863","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:17:15.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_wQlOv992MAoWt1w4H9dMjQ0k|fc_0a7381f2013991140169c87d98221c8191abebeabf7aa476d1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Research practical ways to have separate conversation threads/sessions with the same OpenClaw agent from Telegram, specifically for topic separation. Focus on Telegram capabilities plus OpenClaw session mapping/config. Investigate whether Telegram direct chats can support multiple threads (likely no), whether topics require groups/supergroups, whether multiple bots/accounts/aliases are a workaround, whether different entrypoints like Gateway web can create separate sessions, and whether OpenClaw config like session.dmScope or multiple agents/channels can help. Return a concise, practical answer with recommended options ranked by simplicity and effectiveness for Lucca. Do not modify files.","label":"telegram-separate-conversations-research","runtime":"subagent","model":"anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5","thinking":"off","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace","runTimeoutSeconds":1200,"timeoutSeconds":20,"thread":false,"mode":"run","cleanup":"keep","sandbox":"inherit"},"partialJson":"{\"task\":\"Research practical ways to have separate conversation threads/sessions with the same OpenClaw agent from Telegram, specifically for topic separation. Focus on Telegram capabilities plus OpenClaw session mapping/config. Investigate whether Telegram direct chats can support multiple threads (likely no), whether topics require groups/supergroups, whether multiple bots/accounts/aliases are a workaround, whether different entrypoints like Gateway web can create separate sessions, and whether OpenClaw config like session.dmScope or multiple agents/channels can help. Return a concise, practical answer with recommended options ranked by simplicity and effectiveness for Lucca. Do not modify files